      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters characterized with documented sources; key uncertain inputs identified with ranges.",
      "rationale": "Geometric inputs from CMM measurements with documented tolerances. Fluid property inputs from published literature. Hemolysis model coefficients taken from single-source calibration; no range characterization performed for these coefficients."
    },
