    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been assessed. Seven factors fully meet required levels; six factors show minor gaps (model form at level 2 vs required 3, model inputs at level 3 vs required 4) that are documented and accepted given the validation evidence base. The hemolysis index comparisons across five operating points demonstrate acceptable predictive accuracy for the VAD COU. Assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
